Established Business in Australia visa (subclass 845)The Established Business in Australia visa (subclass 845) closed to new applications on 1 July 2012. You cannot apply for this visa. Information on other business visas is available through the SkillSelect website.
If you have applied for this visa but no visa decision has yet been made, you can add your spouse, defacto partner or dependent children to your application until the visa is decided.
